I'm graduating with a Master's degree in Control Engineering 
from [University of Rome "La Sapienza"][sapienza].

I worked for my bachelor's thesis with prof. [Nardi][nardi] at the [SIED laboratory][sied], a joint effort with Italian Firemen Dpt. for rescue robotics.

Before, I also worked at <a href="http://www.cnr.it">CNR</a> on 
the <a href="http://robocare.istc.cnr.it/">RoboCare</a> project.

I participated in the <a href="http://www.robocup.org">Robocup</a> 
in 2003 (Padua), 2004 [Lisboa][lisboa], [2005 (Osaka)][osaka].

